    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3959711655" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3959711655" />
    <a title="Katia N" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7381993-katia-n"><img alt="Katia N" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1370960553p2/7381993.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3959711655?book_show_action=true">Apr 27, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Katia N" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Katia N" href="/user/show/7381993-katia-n">Katia N</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780143105145" href="/book/show/1576188.The_Street_of_Crocodiles_and_Other_Stories">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3959711655" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3176338648684329426"><i>&quot;My essence is parasite feeding on metaphors - the fact is I let myself be caught so easily by the first appropriate metaphor. Then flying very far, I have to use all my strength to struggle my way back, slowly returning to my present conscience.&quot;</i><br/><br/>Bruno Schulz</span>
  <span id="freeText3176338648684329426" style="display:none"><i>"My essence is parasite feeding on metaphors - the fact is I let myself be caught so easily by the first appropriate metaphor. Then flying very far, I have to use all my strength to struggle my way back, slowly returning to my present conscience."</i><br /><br />Bruno Schulz</span>
  <a data-text-id="3176338648684329426" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


